strings.Value: "Don't deceive yourself. I shall live longer than all of you combined."
"I regret that I cannot help you... and I don't mean just your bodily wounds."
"No one is questioning your strength. Why do you always behave as if someone's trying to offend you?"
"You've a sharp wit. You better rest a bit though, or we'll be piecing you together tomorrow, ha, ha."
"Admit it, you're only saying that because you miss pain as much as pleasure!"
